    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏴‍☠️  Chaotic Party Arr-cade Action for up to 12 players</strong> <strong>🏴‍☠️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Join two rival crews of up to 6 mates as you battle for supremacy on the high seas. Play locally or online, where teams try to steal treasure, defeat enemy captains, or sink ships to win matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our <strong>FREE DEMO </strong>offers online matches (including crossplay) and the first 10 levels of the campaign. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/9889c2d03760b5c2434e28d163f9095b.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b997d95dc4cb0874804eee880cad1660.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b997d95dc4cb0874804eee880cad1660.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b997d95dc4cb0874804eee880cad1660.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic SNES games and modern couch co-op games, Plunder Panic blends retro graphics, arcade action, team-based strategy, and a boatload of  modify-arrs to keep even the crankiest pirates happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/3dfaa0fce2a466f03733263094764dc9.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/38ec15d3ca34aa844f71e761abd9a719.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/38ec15d3ca34aa844f71e761abd9a719.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/38ec15d3ca34aa844f71e761abd9a719.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunder Panic supports flexible team configurations with local, online, and AI-controlled players, making it perfect for casual parties and competitive play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/544961192b2a96f8e3e9b4372c73123e.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b9d5a59d135f53614a6ea8f45c9f278c.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b9d5a59d135f53614a6ea8f45c9f278c.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/b9d5a59d135f53614a6ea8f45c9f278c.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the treacherous, pirate-infested waters in campaign mode! Complete unique objectives across each island, unlocking new items, levels, and modify-arrs along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/65b24201a147a81ee353104382f06e56.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/6d5be5ba15f4c41dc7fb37373090747a.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/6d5be5ba15f4c41dc7fb37373090747a.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/6d5be5ba15f4c41dc7fb37373090747a.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring 18 unique stages, each with dynamic, gameplay-altering effects! Dodge axe-throwing shopkeepers, spear-shooting Vikings, and even a ship-snapping kraken.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/2a6f4d7998e94eb27801d4edef04dba0.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/052ffee93ca121baf1fe767071bb0f90.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/052ffee93ca121baf1fe767071bb0f90.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/052ffee93ca121baf1fe767071bb0f90.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/4b443de105bbefd023f46b7e3b0aa6fd.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/4b443de105bbefd023f46b7e3b0aa6fd.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/4b443de105bbefd023f46b7e3b0aa6fd.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/260d3b824442c943df61fed99e25e719.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/260d3b824442c943df61fed99e25e719.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/260d3b824442c943df61fed99e25e719.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to add more panic? We have boatloads of game modes, items, and modify-arrs to play with. There are endless combinations to explore on our high seas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/678bc6821842e6d8052c990c16da2dc6.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/60b64256931381caa442e1c7d47deead.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/60b64256931381caa442e1c7d47deead.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/60b64256931381caa442e1c7d47deead.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have a crew on another platform? No problem! Plunder Panic features <strong>crossplay</strong> support across 10+ platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/699990a75695e8c12be87eaa9f6dacc2.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.poster.avif?t=1741477315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.webm?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/0f0db33bca684db1b8961763228c131f.mp4?t=1741477315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aspire to be the top pirate in the world? Swashbuckle the competition in ranked online matches! Or prefer to conquer yer couch? Retro-inspired player awards and stats keep you earning plunder to increase your sharable bounty poster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300360/extras/bb196f17e7c817b181c50fb9fb5809d3.webp?t=1741477315\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our coffers are starting to grow with indie acclaim!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IndieCade Audience Choice Award, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAX Rising Showcase winner, Official selection of the Indie MEGABOOTH </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featured at SXSW, PAX East, PAX West, and PAX Rising Online</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
